&quot;Cheese! Petril!  Cheesoid hate self. Why Cheesoid exist? Cheesoid so lonely!&quot;  
This is a figurine inspired by the &quot;Cheesoid&quot; sketch from the British comedy series &quot;That Mitchell and Webb Look.&quot;  
(<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GzzOw2tmb3A" >https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GzzOw2tmb3A</a>)  
Obviously, they own the copyright to this technological marvel.

